smoke-signal-verb = Send Smoke Signal

## UI Window
smoke-signal-window-title = Send Smoke Signal
smoke-signal-window-prompt = Type your message. It will reach all tribe members.
smoke-signal-window-placeholder = Enter message...
smoke-signal-window-send = Send
